channel.title: Divinepk v5
channel.description: I've played runescape classic since the beginning. I recently decided I wanted to mess around with my own server just to try things out. Well, I'm stumped. I read dayles forum online telling me pretty much everything I need to know, but I can't figure out what's wrong. It says both the servers are offline and anytime I try to log in the connection times out. I have my ports set at 43595 and 80, I have wamp, jdk, and apache-ant all downloaded and put where they are supposed to be. The main thing that I'm concerned with I have done wrong, is possibly the pots, or editing the sever run.bat. The apache-ant is correct, but I'm not entirely sure that the java has been put in correctly. Any help would be much appreciated. I'm very new to this and I know I most likely sound nubbish to all of you guys.
